<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想不想聽
我之前在雜誌上<delay8 />看到的占卜結果～！？<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超～不妙的喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不妙？<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
什麼事情很不妙！？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雜誌上面寫著<delay8 />
「你能夠得到想要的東西」喔！<delay40 /><anim id="Thinking" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，是不是超～不妙的呀～！？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雜誌上面寫著<delay8 />
「出門運勢絕佳」喔！<delay40 /><anim id="Thinking" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，是不是超～不妙的呀～！？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="4" />不對啊，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽你這樣說，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這難道<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />不是好事嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後啊，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我出門去購物的時候，<delay8 />
剛好碰到<tag a="110" b="17" />特賣會，<delay8 />
買到了一件超可愛的連身裙！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的是超不妙的對吧～！！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">對呀～<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後<delay20 />我就跑去
<tag a="110" b="12" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />家裡玩<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果我竟然收到了<delay8 />
上個月零用錢不夠，所以買不起的衣服！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是超不妙的啦～！！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />
這到底哪裡不妙了！？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如說是很幸運才對吧！<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">然後呢，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />我穿上那件衣服出門之後，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就恰巧碰到<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，
還被誇說很好看喔～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />占卜的力量，<delay8 />真的超～不妙的！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="SadSpiral" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_3 arg="4" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你現在是在跟我開玩笑嗎！？<anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是呢<20_2 arg="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><delay20 />當我穿上那件衣服出門後，<delay8 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />卻突然開始下雨，
所以我就被淋得溼答答的～！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太相信占卜的結果，<delay8 />真的很不妙呢～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經完全搞不懂，<delay8 />
到底哪個<delay8 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="player" targetSpec="" />才是真的不妙了啦！</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦～！？<delay40 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
你沒在看動畫的嗎～？<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這絕對是人生的一大損失耶～！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />動畫的故事<20_2 arg="4" />進展得太快了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我比較喜歡看漫畫，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />能照自己的步調來！</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好吧，<20_2 arg="3" />那至少讓我借你<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這季我最推的動畫的原作漫畫，<delay8 />
你拿去看看吧～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是這個，<delay20 />《天空與森林的詩篇》！<delay8 /><anim id="Greeting" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喔，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 />好啊，<delay20 />
先謝啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這部<delay8 />有趣嗎？</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />漫畫的話我也可以接受！<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這部<delay8 />有趣嗎？</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 04 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這部<20_2 arg="3" />雖然是以前的作品，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過趁著在社會上又掀起了一波熱潮，<delay8 />
才有機會被做成動畫～！<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="6" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<20_3 arg="3" /><delay20 /><anim id="Eh" target="player" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="8" />
你也知道<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />《空森》這部作品對吧？</message>
	<message label="106_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">校園風格的作品很不錯呢</message>
	<message label="106_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">很感人對吧～</message>
	<message label="106_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我不知道耶……</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我懂我懂～！<20_2 arg="7" /><delay40 />
而且裡面還是<delay8 />採用住宿制的學校呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的妄想<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />完全停不下來呀～！</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯沒錯～！<20_2 arg="7" /><delay40 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />尤其是主角和英雄兩人
煎熬又淒美的戀情……<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看得我都<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />心痛到想哭了呢～！</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你沒聽過喔～！？<delay frames="60" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
那我也順便<anim id="Scheming" target="actor" targetSpec="" />介紹這部作品
給<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />好了～</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">總而言之，<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />
既然<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" />這麼推薦，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就代表這部真的滿有趣的對吧？</message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的超～有趣唷！<delay40 />
你看完之後，<delay8 />
記得也借給<tag a="110" b="4" />看看！<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />順帶一提，<delay8 />這部作品總共有71集，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚點我再把剩下的集數<delay8 />
拿過去<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你家！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什、什麼<tag a="110" b="0" />！？<delay20 />
竟然有這麼多<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><20_3 arg="8" />好吧，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<20_3 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />看來我們只好打起精神，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="player" targetSpec="" />努力把它看完了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">雖然<20_2 arg="2" />我是不太懂啦，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="8" />但連<tag a="110" b="3" />都知道的話，<delay8 />
<20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />就代表這是滿主流的漫畫吧。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯唷～！<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有70集，<delay8 />
我晚點會拿過去的～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="115" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什、什麼<tag a="110" b="0" />！？<delay40 />
竟然有這麼多嗎<tag a="110" b="0" />！<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好吧！<delay20 />男子漢說一不二！<delay40 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我下次休假的時候，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />就來認真看個夠吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="116" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要你先看漫畫，<delay8 />
就能跟上動畫的進度了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以也不要忘記去看動畫喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="117" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然感覺自己好像
完全掉入你的圈套了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我就信你這一回吧！<anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很不妙對吧～！<anim id="SadSpiral" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊啊～！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
這次的「不妙」<delay8 />
又是哪種意思啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你這傢伙的「不妙」
包含太多意思了，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我每次都搞不懂啊！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我就是在說
你這樣子很不妙啦～！<anim id="Worried" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，你應該啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay20 />就是應該多去理解
像我這樣年輕活潑的少女<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都在想些什麼～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 />你這麼說<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了～！！<20_2 arg="3" /><delay40 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />稍微試一下就好，<delay8 />
你要不要模仿我的說話方式看看？<delay8 />
怎麼樣呢？<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那種事<20_2 arg="4" /><delay8 />我怎麼可能做得到啊！<anim id="Shocked" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />你那個口頭禪<tag a="110" b="0" />
如果只學這個「<tag a="110" b="5" />」的話，<delay20 />
就算是我<tag a="110" b="0" />應該也做得到吧？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="207" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />這主意不錯耶！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />透過模仿我的口頭禪，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />感覺就會更理解少女的心喔！</message>
	<message label="208" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「<tag a="110" b="5" />」<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
「<tag a="110" b="5" />」<tag a="110" b="0" />嗎？<delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
嗯……<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像也不壞，<anim id="Clapping" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />但是這樣做，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的就能理解<delay8 />
所謂的「少女心」嗎？<anim id="Assent" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>